{"tid":337984,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"超蓮G.E.M.上廣州陪李蘊過26歲生日","createTime":"2017-07-27T18:44:37.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-28T05:50:33.000Z","uid":72717,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"afad056236c09a5ce2d16f1c83a2819a222efdb5","tid":337984,"uid":72717,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T18:44:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170727/large/1501150846_35af.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170727%2Flarge%2F1501150846_35af.jpg&h=77a0f4d0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n李蘊、超蓮、G.E.M.一向感情好，三個都係1991出世，每逢生日必定約埋慶祝!李蘊自從嫁咗大陸才俊，生埋囡囡羅紫晞後，專心做少奶奶，不過朋友點都要見!<br />\n<br />\n今日係李蘊26歲生日，超蓮同G.E.M.都上咗廣州同佢慶祝生日。剛才李蘊喺微博貼出合照，留言：「每年也有妳們陪我過生日！謝謝妳們！我愛妳們！」G.E.M.喺微博貼舊相，寫道：「上兩個禮拜找回了我18歲時Renee送我的生日卡。一轉眼八年過去了。這些年來你都一直保持那單純的笑聲，當你的朋友真的很幸福很快樂！祝你生日快樂，愛你！」超蓮就留言：「我們永遠愛你，生日快樂幸福少婦！」<br />\n李蘊同超蓮着連身裙晒腿，喺超蓮Ig動態，李蘊抱住囡囡準備上車前，佢哋似一個鐘頭前先食完嘢，超蓮就叫紫晞送飛吻俾契媽，片中見有人喺身邊，似係準備揸車走，估計李蘊老公羅章冠都在場，唔通啲合照就係由佢操刀嘅! <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170727/large/1501150848_5c21.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170727%2Flarge%2F1501150848_5c21.jpg&h=c5c54340&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170727/large/1501150849_477f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170727%2Flarge%2F1501150849_477f.jpg&h=7c56dca7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d12ddb347a222c1cbd71022d959c584e2981eb84","tid":337984,"uid":72717,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T18:45:00.000Z","msg":"李蘊隻腳真係好好J<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"156241d84934c9cbebe50de1c3bd0850b60296a4","tid":337984,"uid":52020,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-28T04:55:45.000Z","msg":"gem真係著到大陸人咁<br />\n條褲柒到仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"501af7373f8cee75181e6c92fc735f65e1b2377f","tid":337984,"uid":2290,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-28T05:50:33.000Z","msg":"佢2個成日搵李蘊<br />\n佢老公點忍得住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}